(149, 1, '2013-08-07 00:31:06', '2013-08-07 00:31:06', 'Useful sites and links to other sources of assistance, including resources available in all our locations.\n<h3> General</h3>\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a title="Lincoln Land Community College" href="http://www.llcc.edu/" target="_blank">Lincoln Land Community College</a></p>\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">LLCC meets the diversity of lifelong learning in our community in a variety of ways. Educational and service opportunities for all ages are offered through adult education and literacy, community education, youth and senior citizen programs and volunteer information. Such activities take place on-campus, in regional education centers around the district and at other key locations as necessary.</p>\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a title="IL Department of Human Services" href="http://www.dhs.state.il.us/page.aspx?" target="_blank">IL Department of Human Services</a></p>\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">DHS can help you and your family meet your basic needs. We offer a range of services to help you become healthy and self-sufficient.</p>\n\n<h3>Springfield</h3>\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a title="Catholic Charities of Springfield" href="http://www.cc.dio.org/area_offices/springfield/home.htm" target="_blank">Catholic Charities of Springfield</a></p>\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Services Provided: St. Clare''s Health Clinic, Crisis Assistance, Family Preservation, Holy Family Food Pantry, MedAssist, Referral Services, St. John''s Breadline</p>\n\n<h3>Litchfield</h3>\n<h3>North Macoupin</h3>\n<h3>Beardstown</h3>', 'More Resources', 'Useful sites and links to other sources of assistance, including resources available in all our locations.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '8-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-08-07 00:31:06', '2013-08-07 00:31:06', '', 8, 'http://localhost:8081/?p=149', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
